trans-unit.source: Represents the <see langword="<ReferenceList>" /> element used in XML encryption.
trans-unit.target: Representa el elemento <see langword="<ReferenceList>" /> utilizado en el cifrado XML.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Esta clase no puede heredarse.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> class represents the `<ReferenceList>` element of an encrypted document XML signature defined by the XML encryption specification.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> clase representa el `<ReferenceList>` elemento de una firma XML de documento cifrado definida por la especificación de cifrado XML.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> class contains references to <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData> and <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> elements that were encrypted by a key contained within another <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> element.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> clase contiene referencias a <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData> y <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> elementos que se cifraron mediante una clave incluida dentro de otra <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> elemento.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> class uses <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.DataReference> elements to reference <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData> elements, and <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.KeyReference> elements to reference <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> elements.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> clase utiliza <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.DataReference> elementos hagan referencia <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData> elementos, y <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.KeyReference> elementos hagan referencia <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> elementos.

trans-unit.source: You can add only <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.DataReference> or <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.KeyReference> objects to the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> collection.
trans-unit.target: Puede agregar solo <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.DataReference> o <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.KeyReference> objetos a la <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.ReferenceList> colección.

trans-unit.source: For more information about XML encryption standards, see http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlenc-core.
trans-unit.target: Para obtener más información acerca de los estándares de cifrado XML, vea http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlenc-core.
